      "content": "it's just constant. like even when i'm home i can't escape it because of social media and everything. i look at people my age and they have like projects and plans and stuff, but when i look ahead i just feel this massive weight in my chest. it's like i'm trapped in a loop of being hated and i just... i can't see a version of my life where this isn't happening. the future just looks like more of this.",
